127
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:40,740
so I couldn't tell you.

128
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:44,410
But you can't be the only one
who doesn't know.

129
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,000
Min-jeong.

130
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:49,170
Believe it or not,

131
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,840
