because of her.

160
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:29,720
I'm just worried about her,
and I feel bad for her.

161
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,600
That's all.

162
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:33,940
Yu-ri is Seo-woo's mom,

163
00:14:34,100 --> 00:14:37,070
