but it's complicated.

164
00:14:38,070 --> 00:14:40,110
That's why I keep sighing.

165
00:14:40,690 --> 00:14:42,740
Gang-hwa and you feel the same way, too.

166
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,370
I understand

167
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:48,660
