169
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:54,790
Why?

170
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:57,340
Everyone is having a hard time
because I came back.

171
00:14:57,420 --> 00:15:00,920
Because of me, Gang-hwa and you
are such in pain.

172
00:15:01,970 --> 00:15:03,550
