836
01:10:18,320 --> 01:10:20,610
Surgery should be performed
based on urgency.

837
01:10:20,700 --> 01:10:23,870
Money shouldn't decide
who gets treated first.

838
01:10:23,950 --> 01:10:27,250
That's my husband. Isn't he amazing?

839
01:10:27,330 --> 01:10:28,660
He really is.

840
01:10:28,960 --> 01:10:30,790
My son-in-law is a real doctor.

841
01:10:31,460 --> 01:10:33,080
You're the best.

842
